data.description: Prime development location in the highly sought after South Austin location. Renovate the current home and add an ADU or tear down and build 2 on this level 11,901 SF lot (.2732 acres), the possibilities are endless. Zoned SF-3. Excellent South Austin neighborhood convenient to everything - less than 5 miles to Downtown, walking distance to coffee shops, grocery stores, restaurants, breweries, and more! This is being sold AS-IS for land value. Buyer to independently verify all information including but not limited to taxes, schools, square footage, lot size, restrictions, zoning, development. If buyer plans to develop lot, they need to do their own independent research. Priced for development well below TCAD Appraisal and RealAVM™/ CoreLogic® derived values. Title open and ready to close. Contact the listing agent for more information.
